WEBVTT

01:38.320 --> 01:40.520
EPISODE 13

01:40.600 --> 01:43.560
It's okay.
Get another long-distance attacker.

01:43.800 --> 01:44.920
It'll be faster.

01:46.000 --> 01:47.320
Okay, I'll put a call out to the clan.

01:47.400 --> 01:48.920
Someone will come.

01:50.920 --> 01:52.560
Anyone want to off Underworld Granny?

01:52.640 --> 01:54.320
Two spots, one shooter and one anything.

01:56.200 --> 01:58.800
Two spots?
Yaoyao and I will be right over.

02:03.880 --> 02:07.360
The weather is terrible today.
Let's call it a day.

02:09.600 --> 02:10.880
No...

02:12.480 --> 02:15.240
What's today? Today, we don't kill.

02:16.200 --> 02:17.280
That's no good.

02:19.920 --> 02:23.320
My stomach hurts! I think I have the runs.

02:25.200 --> 02:27.560
Why doesn't the power go out now?

02:28.400 --> 02:30.800
No, I have to say something.

02:30.880 --> 02:32.880
Somebody has to break
the awkward silence.

02:33.160 --> 02:34.840
Does anyone want out?

02:35.200 --> 02:36.800
Leishen Nini is in our clan.

02:36.880 --> 02:38.200
Why should we leave?

02:38.280 --> 02:40.160
She and Yixiao Naihe should go.

02:59.560 --> 03:00.520
Team up.

03:09.120 --> 03:11.560
Underworld Cave is a six-layer
tree hollow.

03:11.640 --> 03:12.560
The boss of Underworld Cave

03:12.640 --> 03:14.680
is Underworld Granny,
with her male lovers.

03:14.760 --> 03:15.880
The first level is easier.

03:15.960 --> 03:18.240
"Nie Xiaoqian Calling for Help"
is a test of our caliber.

03:18.320 --> 03:20.600
The four levels after are manned
by Underworld Granny's male lovers.

03:20.680 --> 03:21.800
If we send the male lovers running,

03:21.880 --> 03:24.640
we'll reach Underworld Granny
at the last level.

03:24.720 --> 03:26.000
At the last level,

03:26.080 --> 03:29.000
Underworld Granny and her male lovers
will fight together.

04:02.120 --> 04:03.080
I was a respectable woman,

04:03.480 --> 04:05.480
when Underworld Granny
abducted me to this cave,

04:05.560 --> 04:07.800
and made me seduce men for her enjoyment.

04:08.520 --> 04:10.760
I'm grateful
heroes and heroines like you

04:10.840 --> 04:11.840
have come to rescue me.

04:12.600 --> 04:15.200
But I have to test your chops,

04:15.280 --> 04:16.839
in case you can't beat Ghost Granny,

04:16.920 --> 04:18.760
and die for me in vain.

04:43.680 --> 04:46.360
- Help, Zhenshui!
- You should hide.

05:07.000 --> 05:10.840
With your stellar skills,
I'm sure you can beat Underworld Granny,

05:10.920 --> 05:12.080
and rescue innocent folks like me.

05:12.800 --> 05:14.800
I'll lead the way.

05:45.120 --> 05:46.080
Help!

05:47.880 --> 05:49.080
Help!

05:54.880 --> 05:57.040
Zhenshui, I was so scared!

05:57.120 --> 05:59.360
Why are the monsters all after me?

05:59.600 --> 06:01.760
- Stay close to me.
- Okay.

06:01.840 --> 06:03.880
Zhenshui, you're amazing.
You save me every time.

06:07.240 --> 06:08.920
What kind of positioning is that?

06:09.000 --> 06:11.640
That's awful! Running around,
drawing out monsters.

06:11.720 --> 06:14.920
If it weren't for you and Naihe,
our team would've been crushed.

06:15.080 --> 06:17.040
It's fine. We'll take them on
all the same.

06:18.280 --> 06:20.680
I wonder if we can beat
the last level today?

06:21.280 --> 06:25.520
Don't worry. Naihe is here, isn't he?
Right?

06:27.120 --> 06:29.880
Weiwei, I don't envy them at all.

06:29.960 --> 06:31.720
I envy you and Naihe.

06:34.320 --> 06:36.480
That proves you have good judgment.

06:37.160 --> 06:38.560
I have no reply for that.

06:40.280 --> 06:42.280
We're about to reach the last level.
Be careful now.

06:42.360 --> 06:44.680
Underworld Granny is creepy.

06:44.760 --> 06:46.040
If a female player dies,

06:46.120 --> 06:48.240
the system announces
the player died in battle.

06:48.320 --> 06:50.600
If a male player dies,

06:51.160 --> 06:54.880
the player is announced as having
become Underworld Granny's male lover.

06:55.080 --> 06:57.480
Our two male players should watch out.

07:00.080 --> 07:03.200
Heroes and heroines, straight ahead
is Underworld Granny's lair.

07:04.000 --> 07:06.360
That place is full of traps.
I'm afraid to go.

07:07.360 --> 07:11.840
You can go ahead without me.
I'll be leaving now.

07:19.080 --> 07:20.640
The last level is the old woman.

07:20.720 --> 07:21.800
Who'll be in command?

07:26.880 --> 07:29.640
Usually the player with the highest grade
commands the team.

07:36.480 --> 07:39.520
It's okay. This instance dungeon's
difficulty is average.

07:39.920 --> 07:41.560
Lord is harsh.

07:41.760 --> 07:43.800
Zhenshui was going to take the command,

07:44.000 --> 07:45.480
but after what he said,

07:45.560 --> 07:47.680
it'd be hard for Zhenshui to volunteer.

07:47.760 --> 07:51.000
Otherwise, it'd seem like
he's taking advantage of Lord.

07:51.960 --> 07:54.280
I'll do it,
since the difficulty is average.

08:32.320 --> 08:33.760
Another pretty face?

08:34.400 --> 08:38.159
Let me have a taste of you!

08:40.039 --> 08:41.000
She is creepy.

08:41.919 --> 08:44.360
A nymph is in charge?

08:47.160 --> 08:50.640
Don't you know I prefer male flesh?

08:52.680 --> 08:56.320
I'll show you
what Underworld Ghost Granny is made of!

09:08.960 --> 09:11.680
Why did she release monsters
without warning? I wasn't ready!

09:11.760 --> 09:13.640
A female player in the lead
will increase her hatred points,

09:13.720 --> 09:15.080
and monsters will initiate attack.

09:15.480 --> 09:16.720
That's right. I forgot to tell you.

09:17.520 --> 09:20.560
It's fine. I'm used to this creepy game.

09:20.840 --> 09:23.320
Xiaoyu Yaoyao, increase your blood points.

09:25.480 --> 09:26.920
Yinyang Bedlam!

09:51.280 --> 09:54.200
All of my magic has gone dark.
Give me blood, fast!

09:55.720 --> 09:56.560
Naihe?

10:04.320 --> 10:05.320
Doctor, try to dodge attacks.

10:05.400 --> 10:06.720
Once you're hit
I can't improve your condition.

10:13.600 --> 10:15.960
A taste of your own medicine!

10:26.400 --> 10:27.560
Why target me?

10:35.360 --> 10:39.600
Enrich the yin with yang!

11:04.320 --> 11:06.120
Get rid of the nimble male lover.

11:06.200 --> 11:07.640
That skill is so annoying.

11:07.920 --> 11:09.560
- Take charge.
- Okay.

11:18.520 --> 11:21.520
Why? Take out the little monster first.
We'll take one at a time.

11:22.720 --> 11:25.560
Rewards of these rescue instance dungeons,
are determined by the number of survivors.

11:26.080 --> 11:28.160
The male lovers were lured by
Underworld Ghost Granny.

11:28.240 --> 11:30.520
We're rescuing them,
so we can't kill them.

11:31.760 --> 11:33.520
- Archer!
- Got it!

11:43.760 --> 11:44.960
You two work well together.

11:52.640 --> 11:54.200
Awesome! We're about to crack this.

12:25.040 --> 12:27.200
If I use an ultimate to take out the boss,

12:27.560 --> 12:29.160
Zhenshui Wuxiang and Xiaoyu Yaoyao

12:29.240 --> 12:30.840
may not be revived in time.

13:10.640 --> 13:13.960
Amazing! Weiwei,
your Lord is incredible!

13:14.040 --> 13:16.200
How did he do that in such a short time?

13:16.280 --> 13:18.080
He revived Zhenshui and Yaoyao!

13:18.160 --> 13:20.520
He's so magnanimous, so manly!

13:28.320 --> 13:31.320
Nini, we're leaving.
Call me, if you need anything.

13:31.640 --> 13:34.040
If I'm not around, you can look for Naihe.

13:38.200 --> 13:39.480
What? Can I, really?

13:40.520 --> 13:41.360
Yes.

13:45.360 --> 13:47.240
Okay, we're leaving.

13:49.160 --> 13:51.520
Wait! We haven't split up the reward.

13:54.200 --> 13:55.080
It's okay.

14:01.520 --> 14:04.520
Why did you save Zhenshui and Xiaoyu?

14:06.840 --> 14:10.320
Don't you think they'll feel worse,
being saved by me?

14:14.320 --> 14:16.400
Okay, you've convinced me.

14:17.400 --> 14:18.960
What do we do next?

14:21.760 --> 14:24.080
Hold on. I'm on the phone.

14:26.600 --> 14:27.680
On the phone?

14:29.520 --> 14:31.800
Don't tell me, you were on the phone,

14:31.880 --> 14:33.360
while we were fighting the boss?

14:36.320 --> 14:37.160
Yes.

14:45.320 --> 14:47.320
How do you maneuver with one hand?

14:49.800 --> 14:50.720
Headphones.

14:55.040 --> 14:58.280
That's right, you can be on the phone
with headphones.

14:58.560 --> 15:00.120
I'm so silly.

15:00.960 --> 15:02.440
Go take your call.

15:07.240 --> 15:09.360
He was on the phone while playing,

15:09.560 --> 15:11.560
and he delivered such great maneuvers.

15:11.960 --> 15:15.760
I think the skills of Lord
are extraordinary.

15:17.120 --> 15:18.160
I see.

15:24.360 --> 15:25.240
See you in two days.

15:31.480 --> 15:35.160
Right, I should hurry up and finish
the gift for Lord.

15:35.600 --> 15:40.720
I hope I can make super equipment.
It's time to boost my standing.

15:45.520 --> 15:46.360
Weiwei?

15:52.720 --> 15:53.560
Are you done?

15:54.720 --> 15:57.240
Yes, I'll go on a business trip
in two days.

16:12.680 --> 16:13.640
Look at this.

16:28.520 --> 16:30.360
Looks like the department belle was here.

16:32.360 --> 16:35.240
Say, if Ashuang finds out

16:35.320 --> 16:37.760
this all-male sanctuary

16:37.840 --> 16:39.520
has been dirtied by Mrs. Nai,

16:39.760 --> 16:41.040
will it kill his ability
to write programs?

16:42.720 --> 16:44.280
That's for sure.

16:44.640 --> 16:47.280
Listen, I'm going to tell him,

16:47.520 --> 16:51.240
we've all stayed single,
because of this guy.

16:53.760 --> 16:54.720
Nai,

16:56.960 --> 16:59.840
Zhenyi hasn't contacted me since.

17:01.240 --> 17:05.040
Do you think they found out
I've pledged to give myself to you?

17:06.480 --> 17:09.480
Bro, you're so bad with idioms.

17:09.560 --> 17:11.200
Will you stop already?

17:11.440 --> 17:14.319
I'm seriously intrigued.
How did you get into Qing University?

17:14.880 --> 17:17.839
With this, of course.

17:19.000 --> 17:19.960
Fine...

17:20.040 --> 17:23.440
Zhenyi stopped contacting you,
because Fengteng stepped in.

17:25.400 --> 17:27.680
They backed off so easily?

17:28.040 --> 17:31.880
That's boring. I was hoping
Nai would do something to Zhenyi.

17:33.560 --> 17:36.360
Fengteng gave us pretty good feedback
on the mobile game.

17:36.440 --> 17:38.720
We should get a clear answer tomorrow.

17:39.720 --> 17:40.920
So, our imperative

17:41.640 --> 17:44.120
is to get the rights to develop
"A New Chinese Ghost Story."

17:45.560 --> 17:48.080
Mrs. Nai sold the video

17:48.160 --> 17:49.600
and got rare monsters for us.

17:49.880 --> 17:51.880
Fengteng seems to love this idea.

17:52.080 --> 17:54.000
If we use this as leverage,

17:54.080 --> 17:55.240
would it help the collaboration?

17:56.040 --> 17:57.800
It's not a decisive concept.

17:57.880 --> 17:59.520
It won't sway Fengteng's decision.

18:00.320 --> 18:04.040
The gameplay of marriage by abduction
can be super complex and interesting.

18:04.120 --> 18:05.800
It needs the support
of a more powerful engine,

18:06.400 --> 18:08.240
to further demonstrate our advantage.

18:08.600 --> 18:11.000
We're prepared. Zhenyi is not.

18:17.200 --> 18:20.400
Of course, it also made Weiwei happy.

18:25.080 --> 18:26.240
Now I get it.

18:26.760 --> 18:28.400
That was the real point.

18:31.640 --> 18:32.880
We must secure the right

18:33.680 --> 18:36.840
to develop "A New Chinese Ghost Story"
when you visit Fengteng this time.

18:37.040 --> 18:38.400
By any means necessary.

18:39.320 --> 18:41.360
No problem, Mr. Zhen. Don't worry.

18:41.440 --> 18:43.280
Our R&D capabilities are obvious to all.

18:43.520 --> 18:45.760
I'm 100 percent confident,
we'll get this project.

18:46.320 --> 18:49.040
But I hear Zhiyi Tech

18:49.120 --> 18:50.920
has expressed interest, too.

18:51.240 --> 18:55.040
- What? Those college kids?
- Yes.

18:55.120 --> 18:56.720
Aren't they trying to bite off
more than they can chew?

19:05.000 --> 19:08.480
Well, to be on the safe side,

19:08.560 --> 19:10.240
I'll go with you this time.

19:10.600 --> 19:11.880
Prepare some gifts.

19:11.960 --> 19:14.520
- Send them to Fengteng's CEO, Mr. Wang.
- Got it.

19:14.840 --> 19:17.840
You can covertly raise the kickback, too.

19:18.160 --> 19:19.240
Okay.

19:20.000 --> 19:22.800
Profit is secondary for this project.

19:23.040 --> 19:26.440
The key is to use Fengteng Technology,

19:26.520 --> 19:28.920
to elevate our status
in the gaming industry

19:29.560 --> 19:31.440
and expand our influence.

19:33.560 --> 19:36.320
I'm sure
when the collaboration is announced,

19:36.400 --> 19:38.400
our stock price will go up.

19:38.720 --> 19:40.680
When that happens,
we'll get everything back.

19:41.080 --> 19:42.200
Got it, Mr. Zhen.

19:46.000 --> 19:47.240
Zhen Shaoxiang!

19:48.240 --> 19:50.720
I put you here at the office to learn,

19:50.800 --> 19:51.960
not to play on your phone!

19:52.040 --> 19:55.800
Look at you!
Even your younger cousin is more mature.

19:57.680 --> 20:01.640
I was listening! Isn't it about the right
to develop "A New Chinese Ghost Story"?

20:01.720 --> 20:04.040
If we get this project,
it'll expand our influence.

20:04.120 --> 20:07.120
We'll sell, when the stock price goes up.
What's so hard about it?

20:07.480 --> 20:08.320
Hey...

20:08.600 --> 20:11.600
All you talk is nonsense.
You're coming with me tomorrow.

20:12.920 --> 20:14.960
Fengteng is holding
a very important banquet tomorrow night.

20:15.720 --> 20:17.520
All the business leaders will attend.

20:17.800 --> 20:19.360
You're coming with me, to meet them.

20:20.200 --> 20:23.280
Dad, I have an exam tomorrow.
I'll go next time.

20:34.200 --> 20:35.840
I don't get Xiao Nai.

20:35.960 --> 20:39.080
What does Bei Weiwei have
that Yiran doesn't?

20:39.200 --> 20:42.400
She's beautiful and talented.
Plus, she met Xiao Nai first.

20:42.480 --> 20:44.600
Who met whom first isn't the point.

20:44.680 --> 20:48.840
Yiran is too naive.
She's not as manipulative as Bei Weiwei.

20:52.040 --> 20:55.280
It's all your roommate's fault.

20:55.480 --> 20:56.600
You took too many detours.

20:58.440 --> 21:00.080
Can I still get back on track?

21:01.360 --> 21:05.480
Sure, but you're not to take
the initiative.

21:05.560 --> 21:08.880
You're to use your elegance and beauty,

21:09.280 --> 21:13.200
to attract him into pursuing you.
That's the right track.

21:13.720 --> 21:16.360
Your roommate's ideas
of chasing him around

21:16.920 --> 21:20.120
were below you and totally inappropriate.

21:20.360 --> 21:22.080
You should know who you are.

21:22.520 --> 21:24.280
You're a well-to-do girl,

21:24.480 --> 21:26.680
not a common girl, like Bei Weiwei.

21:26.960 --> 21:28.440
That makes sense, Yiran.

21:28.520 --> 21:30.600
Why don't you listen to Ai Chanel?

21:33.280 --> 21:34.640
Attend Fengteng's banquet.

21:35.240 --> 21:38.600
Use every opportunity you have
to make contact with Xiao Nai.

21:39.640 --> 21:43.560
Remember, be yourself.
Show off your positive traits.

21:44.240 --> 21:47.560
Do not make the first move, by any means.
He will notice you.

22:05.280 --> 22:08.280
Your flight's at nine,
and you're having breakfast on campus?

22:08.440 --> 22:09.280
It's seven now.

22:12.200 --> 22:13.400
School's breakfast is delicious.

22:15.080 --> 22:17.040
But you're about to graduate.

22:17.120 --> 22:19.680
They'll take away your cafeteria card,
and you won't be able to dine here.

22:21.400 --> 22:22.320
You have one.

22:25.800 --> 22:27.520
What if I don't lend it to you?

22:29.920 --> 22:31.080
Then I'll have to be a freeloader.

22:33.800 --> 22:35.040
Use my parents' cards.

22:38.720 --> 22:40.720
How can you be so blunt
about being a freeloader?

22:52.160 --> 22:54.680
I have Professor Xiao's class today.

22:55.200 --> 22:56.240
It's the last class of the semester.

22:57.720 --> 23:01.280
Um... Does he know about us?

23:02.800 --> 23:03.760
Oh.

23:06.280 --> 23:07.720
What does "oh" mean?

23:07.800 --> 23:09.400
Is that a yes or no?

23:10.760 --> 23:13.440
We're turning in our term paper today.
Will he be there?

23:16.800 --> 23:19.120
He wasn't going to, but he will.

23:22.400 --> 23:23.880
That means he knows?

23:26.320 --> 23:28.960
I should've asked you to look at my paper.

23:29.080 --> 23:32.680
If my paper's bad
will he have a bad impression of me?

23:34.360 --> 23:37.280
This is a straightforward thing.
You don't need to be nervous.

23:39.160 --> 23:44.800
- How?
- Just... Pretend you don't know him.

24:08.920 --> 24:11.080
Did you see that girl? How is she?

24:12.360 --> 24:13.640
Exceptional.

24:15.920 --> 24:19.240
This is her paper. You can take a look.

24:20.120 --> 24:21.360
Nice penmanship.

24:22.240 --> 24:24.320
And her logic is very precise.

24:26.160 --> 24:27.800
She's probably quite smart.

24:31.920 --> 24:33.320
That's very nice.

24:33.400 --> 24:35.600
Their department chair's house
is next to ours.

24:35.680 --> 24:38.320
She's very strict
with the female students.

24:38.880 --> 24:41.440
If she thinks she's good, then she's good.

24:47.600 --> 24:51.120
I knew Xiao Nai was up to something.

24:51.360 --> 24:54.240
When he suddenly showed up to my class,

24:54.920 --> 24:57.080
he sat right next to that girl.

24:59.200 --> 25:02.240
Our son takes after neither you nor me.

25:02.560 --> 25:05.160
When you fell for me,

25:05.240 --> 25:07.600
you kept your feelings hidden
for five or six years.

25:08.880 --> 25:10.840
What do you mean?

25:10.920 --> 25:13.080
You were the one who fell for me, okay?

25:13.480 --> 25:17.480
You kept your feelings hidden for
five or six... No, eight or nine years!

25:18.480 --> 25:20.840
I thought it would kill you.
That's why I approached you.

25:23.080 --> 25:25.440
Don't flatter yourself!

25:25.520 --> 25:28.120
You would've cried if I turned you down.

25:29.160 --> 25:33.840
What's this nonsense?
Do you have any evidence?

25:35.520 --> 25:38.040
Enough... Don't beat a dead horse.

25:39.240 --> 25:41.240
Who does our son take after anyway?

25:42.080 --> 25:44.520
He's got a girlfriend
right out of college.

25:44.800 --> 25:46.160
That's not like either of us.

25:49.520 --> 25:55.000
Maybe us two negatives
make a positive?

25:58.920 --> 25:59.920
That's probably it.

26:18.280 --> 26:19.280
Excuse me!

26:27.200 --> 26:28.760
Lord may not be here,

26:28.840 --> 26:30.920
but you don't have to sigh,
when you eat with us.

26:31.560 --> 26:35.040
I wasn't, I was just thinking,
there are so many people,

26:35.120 --> 26:36.920
will there be any food left for us?

26:40.120 --> 26:44.760
Weiwei, how's your progress
with Lord?

26:46.160 --> 26:48.320
- Meeting parents.
- So soon?

26:48.720 --> 26:51.800
Kidding!
We've only known each other for a week.

26:51.880 --> 26:53.320
How can we progress so fast?

26:53.440 --> 26:56.160
I meant, I just had
Professor Xiao's class today.

26:56.840 --> 26:59.240
You two sealed the deal
after meeting for two hours.

26:59.320 --> 27:00.320
At this rate,

27:00.400 --> 27:02.840
it's not odd to meet his parents,
after knowing him for a week.

27:03.320 --> 27:07.080
I didn't meet his parents, I swear.

27:07.240 --> 27:09.360
Why do I have to partake in this teasing?

27:10.800 --> 27:12.320
No way!

27:12.440 --> 27:16.240
Is Lord Xiao changing tactics,
and slowing down?

27:16.840 --> 27:20.400
Maybe he's pulling
"the boiling frog" trick?

27:21.680 --> 27:23.760
He must want a long-term relationship
with Weiwei.

27:23.840 --> 27:25.760
So romantic!

27:26.440 --> 27:29.160
- You're the frog.
- That must be the case.

27:29.600 --> 27:33.200
Bring it to a boil, then simmer on low.

27:33.280 --> 27:35.720
Sooner or later,
he'll swallow you, the frog.

27:36.440 --> 27:39.080
I think Lord's game plan is

27:39.160 --> 27:42.360
first a blitz then infiltration.

27:42.680 --> 27:46.320
When are you going to engage
in a protracted struggle, Weiwei?

27:46.400 --> 27:50.280
Right! First, it's howling winds
and torrential rain, to disorient you.

27:50.560 --> 27:55.200
Then, it's light breeze
and drizzling rain, to make you dizzy.

27:55.800 --> 27:57.560
What's the last kind of rain?

27:59.360 --> 28:01.120
"Sex in the rain"?

28:07.040 --> 28:09.680
Protracted struggle...

28:09.760 --> 28:12.800
It's about performance and endurance...

28:20.920 --> 28:24.440
Mrs. Nai, I'm Mo Zha Ta.

28:26.800 --> 28:29.600
- Mo Zha Ta?
- Yes... It's me...

28:32.200 --> 28:36.680
No way! That means he overheard
our conversation?

28:37.080 --> 28:38.560
That's so embarrassing...

28:38.760 --> 28:43.200
Didn't he say he had a dark tan?

28:46.200 --> 28:49.880
- So, it's Mr. Girly!
- No!

28:59.880 --> 29:01.000
Nice to meet you.

29:04.080 --> 29:07.040
- It's Xiaoling's comedy hour again.
- He said, "Mulan, I love you."

29:07.120 --> 29:08.520
"How did you know I'm a girl?"

29:08.600 --> 29:12.280
- "What? You're a girl?"
- Is it that funny?

29:12.400 --> 29:14.040
Can't you say something
Sisi will understand?

29:30.600 --> 29:32.280
Your wife said something naughty to me.

29:45.200 --> 29:48.040
Enjoy it. I don't mind.

29:53.960 --> 29:57.000
He's totally on her side.

29:58.400 --> 30:00.040
I'll get my revenge!

30:19.720 --> 30:22.000
I thought you came for the mobile game.

30:22.080 --> 30:24.760
I had no idea you have bigger ambitions.

30:24.840 --> 30:28.120
You're interested in developing
"A New Chinese Ghost Story," too?

30:29.360 --> 30:32.760
At the moment, mobile game's
gameplay and presentation

30:32.840 --> 30:34.480
are still very limited.

30:35.040 --> 30:37.200
We wouldn't stop at mobile games.

30:37.280 --> 30:39.640
Our engine is designed for client games.

30:40.440 --> 30:42.960
Fengteng Technology has shifted strategy.

30:43.880 --> 30:47.080
The team behind "A Chinese Ghost Story"
has been transferred to the new market.

30:47.160 --> 30:48.800
Only a maintenance team is left.

30:49.200 --> 30:51.440
We weren't going to launch
"A New Chinese Ghost Story,"

30:51.720 --> 30:54.400
but gamers have been pushing for us
to develop a new version.

30:56.600 --> 31:00.320
We'd rather go without,
than settle for less.

31:01.840 --> 31:04.800
Since your engine is already mature,

31:05.280 --> 31:07.600
then I hope in three months' time,

31:07.680 --> 31:10.400
you can give me a demonstration
that showcases your technical ability,

31:10.680 --> 31:12.560
as well as a more detailed
business proposal,

31:12.640 --> 31:15.160
development schedule,
and a budget plan.

31:15.520 --> 31:17.160
I'm not asking too much, right?

31:21.120 --> 31:23.680
It is asking a lot,
in such a short period of time.

31:24.280 --> 31:26.760
But, we love to rise to the challenge.

31:27.200 --> 31:29.080
Great! We'll wait and see.

31:29.360 --> 31:32.720
As for the mobile game,
Fengteng wants exclusive rights.

31:32.960 --> 31:36.560
If possible, five more percentage points
in terms of revenue share.

31:36.800 --> 31:38.400
I hope you can consider it.

31:50.800 --> 31:54.120
I have great trust
in Fengteng's distribution.

31:54.240 --> 31:57.520
I especially admire Fengteng's
open attitude in terms of collaboration,

31:57.600 --> 31:59.080
allowing each partner

31:59.160 --> 32:01.000
to find the way that suits him best.

32:02.440 --> 32:03.880
I get what you're saying.

32:04.080 --> 32:08.280
What if we throw in Fengteng's superb

32:08.400 --> 32:09.240
promotion resources?

32:11.560 --> 32:12.560
Exclusive distribution for a year.

32:13.800 --> 32:16.280
Mobile games only last for a year.

32:16.360 --> 32:18.000
This offer is meaningless.

32:19.160 --> 32:22.120
I have complete confidence in our product.

32:23.960 --> 32:27.360
All right, it's a deal.

32:27.680 --> 32:29.880
I will push to expedite the contracts.

32:33.480 --> 32:35.560
It's late. The banquet is starting.

32:35.640 --> 32:36.880
Shall we?

32:38.560 --> 32:40.520
I'll introduce you to President Feng.

32:40.600 --> 32:42.400
- Thanks, Mr. Wang.
- This way.

33:08.560 --> 33:10.960
- Hello?
- Hello, Ms. Weiwei?

33:12.880 --> 33:14.920
Are you super disappointed
it's not Nai calling?

33:16.000 --> 33:18.600
Yes, I'm very disappointed.
I'll hang up now.

33:18.680 --> 33:19.840
Don't...

33:21.200 --> 33:25.360
Weiwei, log on
and send us the rare monsters!

33:26.480 --> 33:29.800
No, you'll have to wait
until I'm done studying.

33:30.200 --> 33:31.120
What's more,

33:31.200 --> 33:33.240
it's wrong to distract a student
cramming for exams.

33:33.880 --> 33:35.800
Ms. Weiwei, when Nai comes back,

33:35.880 --> 33:37.560
he'll help you study.

33:38.720 --> 33:40.400
He's already helping me.

33:42.320 --> 33:44.400
Well... That's great...

33:44.720 --> 33:45.960
A lovey-dovey comeback again.

33:46.960 --> 33:48.400
Well then, Weiwei,

33:48.760 --> 33:52.000
we wish you success in the study session.
We won't bother you now.

33:52.080 --> 33:53.360
Remember to send us the rare monsters.

33:53.880 --> 33:57.200
Okay, you guys just wait
in my and Naihe's home.

34:07.400 --> 34:10.440
I wonder how Lord's
business trip is going?

34:11.560 --> 34:14.040
Stop it. Focus on studying.

34:31.960 --> 34:33.000
Okay, go ahead.

34:37.639 --> 34:38.560
All right.

34:40.880 --> 34:42.159
Okay, I get it.

34:43.960 --> 34:45.520
Your wife bullied me.

34:49.199 --> 34:52.679
Looks like you're all having fun,
while I'm gone.

34:53.840 --> 34:55.040
Okay, I understand.

34:58.080 --> 34:59.560
I just heard,

34:59.760 --> 35:02.360
Mr. Zhen from Zhenyi Tech
is attending the banquet, too.

35:03.320 --> 35:06.400
They also seem to be very confident
about "A New Chinese Ghost Story."

35:10.480 --> 35:14.520
I hear there's a bit of animosity
between you and Mr. Zhen?

35:15.640 --> 35:18.280
He's more senior in the industry
we both call home.

35:18.840 --> 35:21.080
It was my honor to get to know him.

35:22.240 --> 35:25.000
Good. That's a great attitude, young man.

36:36.120 --> 36:36.960
Ms. Meng,

36:37.040 --> 36:38.840
your clothes are ready.

36:38.920 --> 36:41.480
If you need anything, do let us know.

36:59.440 --> 37:01.680
Hurry up, Yiran.

37:02.120 --> 37:04.720
Okay, give me 15 more minutes.

37:23.240 --> 37:26.880
- Mr. Zhen, it's time.
- Okay.

37:31.360 --> 37:33.680
Yiran, we're heading down first.

37:33.760 --> 37:36.840
Join us later.
It's the banquet hall on the third floor.

37:37.520 --> 37:39.560
Got it, Uncle. You guys go ahead.

38:26.360 --> 38:28.480
Mr. Xiao, let me introduce you.

38:28.560 --> 38:32.480
This is Mr. He, product director
of "A Chinese Ghost Story."

38:32.560 --> 38:35.240
He, this is Xiao Nai,
the CEO of Zhiyi Tech.

38:36.560 --> 38:38.080
- Mr. He.
- Mr. Xiao.

38:38.240 --> 38:39.680
The mobile game we just signed

38:39.760 --> 38:41.240
was developed by their team.

38:41.680 --> 38:43.840
You two should get to know each other.

38:43.920 --> 38:44.760
Also,

38:45.040 --> 38:49.040
Mr. Xiao is interested in developing
"A New Chinese Ghost Story."

38:50.760 --> 38:54.040
Mr. Xiao is so young.
You remind me of myself, a few years back.

38:54.320 --> 38:56.720
Mr. Wang still loves to
invest in young people.

39:04.560 --> 39:06.720
We talked to Mr. Wang yesterday.

39:06.800 --> 39:08.840
The situation isn't ideal.

39:09.000 --> 39:11.920
He seems a bit inflexible.

39:15.240 --> 39:17.240
He can't make all the decisions.

39:18.720 --> 39:20.800
The game's original manager is key.

39:24.440 --> 39:25.960
Try to talk to others.

39:29.120 --> 39:32.360
Okay, I'll talk to Mr. He in a bit.

39:33.800 --> 39:36.280
Don't wait. Let's go over now.

39:37.200 --> 39:38.040
Okay.

39:48.680 --> 39:50.080
Mr. Wang! Mr. He!

39:50.760 --> 39:53.160
When did you get here, Mr. Zhen?

39:53.240 --> 39:54.840
I didn't see you, when I got here.

39:55.240 --> 39:58.120
Such an eagle eye, Mr. Wang.

39:58.200 --> 40:00.560
You noticed that I was a little late.

40:05.040 --> 40:06.760
Isn't this Mr. Xiao from Zhiyi?

40:08.200 --> 40:10.920
What a coincidence to run into you here!

40:11.600 --> 40:15.640
I heard your mobile game has reached
an agreement with Mr. Wang?

40:16.880 --> 40:18.440
You're well informed.

40:21.320 --> 40:23.880
This collaboration will transform you.

40:24.720 --> 40:27.680
You'll no longer be the team
that could be bought with three million.

40:33.040 --> 40:34.280
Three million?

40:36.200 --> 40:38.960
Mr. Zhen is known in the industry
for his generosity.

40:39.040 --> 40:41.720
We're newcomers,
startled by Mr. Zhen's offer.

40:41.800 --> 40:44.160
We were worried about disappointing,
so we never reached a deal.

40:56.640 --> 40:58.920
Entertain our guests.

40:59.000 --> 41:02.280
I'll take Mr. Xiao to meet President Feng.
This way, please.

41:10.480 --> 41:11.320
President Feng!

41:11.720 --> 41:13.320
This is Xiao Nai,

41:13.400 --> 41:15.440
CEO of Zhiyi Tech,
whom I've told you about.

41:15.520 --> 41:17.600
He's the top student from
Qing University's computer department.

41:17.680 --> 41:19.680
Mr. Xiao, this is President Feng.

41:20.200 --> 41:21.520
Nice to have finally met you,
President Feng.

41:22.880 --> 41:25.320
Mr. Xiao is much younger
than I anticipated.

41:25.400 --> 41:28.160
Yes, I'd worried Mr. Xiao was too young,

41:28.240 --> 41:29.320
but I've been very impressed,

41:29.640 --> 41:30.920
both in terms of the mobile game

41:31.000 --> 41:32.200
and the proposal for
"A New Chinese Ghost Story."

41:32.800 --> 41:36.080
What's more, Mr. Xiao is also
very knowledgeable in system security.

41:37.560 --> 41:40.440
So, you're also interested in
developing "A New Chinese Ghost Story"?

41:41.040 --> 41:43.440
"A Chinese Ghost Story" is a quality game.

41:43.520 --> 41:45.360
I hope to expand upon the fine basis

41:45.440 --> 41:46.560
built by those before us.

41:47.760 --> 41:49.400
My wife plays this game, too.

41:49.480 --> 41:50.840
So she's invested in the project.

41:51.840 --> 41:54.960
I haven't been happy with
a number of proposals so far.

41:55.560 --> 41:56.880
I look forward to be moved by you.

41:57.600 --> 41:59.000
You won't be disappointed.

42:00.040 --> 42:01.160
I can't wait.

44:45.560 --> 44:48.000
Subtitle translation by Lu Yuhan
